{"tid":1952678,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（Econ高手請入）大通脹 vs 大通縮","createTime":"2020-03-31T17:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T09:38:53.000Z","uid":294404,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"061b223360ae530bb1d12a87d2e1b1237e188da8","tid":1952678,"uid":294404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:55:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200330/PR7DEPPCPAUPQHDC64EPLP6YDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200330%2FPR7DEPPCPAUPQHDC64EPLP6YDA%2F&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhoBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=4ef4c1be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200330%2FPR7DEPPCPAUPQHDC64EPLP6YDA%2F&h=c61d2edf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200330/PR7DEPPCPAUPQHDC64EPLP6YDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n【大棋局】大通脹 Vs 大通縮（Mr. Tregunter）<br />\n<br />\n//美國亦公佈推2萬億美元經濟刺激方案，貨幣政策及財政政策都做晒，已冇晒子彈。政府想托股價，港股美股未彈完，但亦未見底。<br />\n<br />\n春耕秋收，四季有時。疫情誤時，停工減產，只會令各類物資存量減少。埃及暫停豆類出口，哈薩克斯坦停出口小麥、糖，塞爾維亞停出口葵花籽油，越南趑趄於是否停出口白米&hellip;&hellip;唔等使之物需求會下跌，但必需品需求不會跌，再遇上供應減少就係完美通脹。<br />\n<br />\n周期末段+石油戰+武漢肺炎+需求下降，係大通縮；疫情誤農時+停工減產+供應下跌+無限QE，係大通脹。我們即將要面對一個精神分裂的時代，大通脹與大通縮兩股力量在較勁。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通漲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通縮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f26e8a7424975b3b4e1dd15518397afbb1d3dc","tid":1952678,"uid":314136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"打和 super"},{"pid":"0d186a2106c4cb94451e5135676c7587a75f844d","tid":1952678,"uid":219742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:03:42.000Z","msg":"通脹係計CPI ,  咁你話呢"},{"pid":"cf61a38138c688b04877198daf59996fe172ae3b","tid":1952678,"uid":294404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d186a2106c4cb94451e5135676c7587a75f844d","tid":1952